(N'XE_BUFFERMGR_ALLPROCESSED_EVENT',N'TRACING_XEVENTS',2,0,N'Occurs when Extended Events session buffers are flushed to targets. This wait occurs on a background thread.',N'Extended Events oder SQL Trace.',N'Dispatcher-Idle-Waits sind meist benign; aktive Target-Probleme können Events verzögern.',N'Benign-Flag, Sessionstatus, Target-Latenz und Eventverlust prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
