(N'XE_DISPATCHER_CONFIG_SESSION_LIST',N'TRACING_XEVENTS',2,0,N'Occurs when an Extended Events session that is using asynchronous targets is started or stopped. This wait indicates either of the following: An Extended Events session is registering with a background thread pool.',N'Extended Events oder SQL Trace.',N'Dispatcher-Idle-Waits sind meist benign; aktive Target-Probleme können Events verzögern.',N'Benign-Flag, Sessionstatus, Target-Latenz und Eventverlust prüfen.',N'REFERENCE_NORMALIZED',N'IMPORTED_REVIEW_REQUIRED'),
